name: Ordinal Snakes Club: Silver Snakes
description: Ordinal Snakes Club, under new management, come see what we can build! Silver Snakes are the second collection of Ordinal Snakes Club, check out 'Ordinal Snakes Club: Golden Snakes' as well! Be careful! There are Ordinals that look like Ordinal Snakes that are inscribed around the same time, but aren't included in the collection and don't provide any utility!
